                <TextView
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:text="       We fall ill because we leading lives against nature. Even if our individual organs work well, it is the proper integration of the individual functions they perform that maintains proper health.  Nature has always been the best healer. It is so gentle and yet very effective. It teaches us about ourselves, our powers, our immune systems. Natural healing deals with the cause of our maladies and not just the effects. It believes in the mantra – prevention is better than cure. It involves simple things – an agile lifestyle, fresh home food, healthy living habits, undisturbed rest. These things build up our ability to heal and maintain our health.
"
